    "content": "<html>\n<head>\n    <title>Dynamic Programming Example</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>Dynamic Programming Example</h1>\n    <h2>Problem: 1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + 5 = ?</h2>\n    <p>Manual calculation: 1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + 5 = 15</p>\n    <p>Dynamic Programming Solution:</p>\n    <p>1. Initialize an array dp with 5 elements, all set to 0.</p>\n    <p>2. Iterate through the numbers 1 to 5.</p>\n    <p>3. For each number i, calculate dp[i] as the sum of dp[i - 1] and i.</p>\n    <p>4. Return dp[5] as the result.</p>\n\n    <h2>Code: <code>javascript</code></h2>\n    <pre>\n        <script>\n            function dp(i, dp) {\n                if (i === 0) {\n                    dp[0] = 0;\n                } else {\n                    dp[i] = dp[i - 1] + i;\n                }\n                return dp[i];\n            }\n\n            let result = 0;\n            let dpArr = new Array(6).fill(0);\n\n            // Initialize dpArr\n            for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {\n                dpArr[i] = dp(i, dpArr);\n            }\n\n            // Print the result\n            console.log(dpArr[5]);\n\n            // Dynamic Programming Solution\n            function dynamicProgramming(i, dp) {\n                if (i === 0) {\n                    return 0;\n                } else {\n                    return dp[i] = dp[i - 1] + i;\n                }\n            }\n\n            result = dynamicProgramming(5, dpArr);\n\n            console.log(\"Dynamic Programming Solution:\", result);\n        </script>\n    </pre>\n</body>\n</html>"
